Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬路瑞希无论做什么事情都很热心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也在专业书籍上  调查自己不懂的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何递送情书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.30,0:00:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是亲手递送最好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能更好地传达心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到好的答复的可能性也会变大…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬路同学  你在学习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉井君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.90,0:00:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  有些问题不太懂所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  现在鼓起勇气把情书递给他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉…吉井君  其实…是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你千万不要笑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该笑哪里才好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//-------------------OPJP--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:03.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放っといて育つものなんだ　なんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:05.15,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one more chance, one more chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:06.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one more chance, one more chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:22.35,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出会いましては簡単すぎるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.00,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初に決めた答えはひとつ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ときめきました合格しますか?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.00,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋も勝負もあわてない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:32.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,コツコツコツと徹夜に溜息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私のなかに天才dreamer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:38.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うことみな叶えばいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:40.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人の世界はきにしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:43.00,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect-area complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:45.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対ここで待ってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:52.25,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect-area　望む声が聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.50,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah! EAR EAR!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:56.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?　とまらないすれちがい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:59.45,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私が相談相手なら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「友達かい?」「友達です。」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しき0点だね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:07.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No!　やりなおしかきなおし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本気で　one more chance please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:13.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまより素敵な未来があるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:20.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまより素敵に　my life, my life, my life!!
